com.facebook.buck.features.project.intellij.model

Class IjModuleAndroidFacet

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.facebook.buck.features.project.intellij.model.IjModuleAndroidFacet

  • public abstract class IjModuleAndroidFacet
extends Object
    The information necessary to add the Android facet to the module. This essentially means the Java code in the given module is written against the Android SDK.
